num1 = int(input("Enter first number: "))
num2 = int(input("Enter second number: "))
num3 = int(input("Enter third number: "))

if (num1 >= num2) and(num1 >= num3):
 print(" num1 is largest number:", num1) 
elif (num2 >= num1) and (num2 >= num3):
   print(" num 2 is largest number:", num2) 
else:
   print("  num3 is largest number:", num3)
Step 1 : start the program
Step 2: declare variable num 1, num2, num3, largest value.
Step 3: if num 1> num 2 go to step 4 otherwise go to step 5 
Step 4: if num 1>num 3 SET largest value =num1 otherwise largest value = num 3 
Step 5: if num 2> num 3 SET largest value= num 2 otherwise largest value= num 3
Step 6: end
